!iflang [english]

!begin_node vqt_name_and_id

(!begin_liste) [Availability]

!item [Name:]
ØInquire face name and ID by nameÆ - Search for font ID and name.

!item [Opcode:]
230 (Sub-Opcode 100)

!item [Syntax:]
int16_t vqt_name_and_id ( int16_t handle, int16_t font_format,
                       int8_t *font_name, int8_t *ret_name );

!item [Description:]
The call vqt_name_and_id searches for a font with a given name and format.
The following apply:

!begin_xlist !short [font_format]
!item [Parameter]
Meaning
!item [~]
~
!item [handle]
Workstation identifier
!item [font_format]
Desired font format:
!begin_xlist Short
!item [1 =]
Bitmap font
!item [2 =]
Speedo font
!item [4 =]
TrueType font
!item [8 =]
Type-1 font
!end_xlist
!item [font_name]
Desired font name
!item [ret_name]
Name of the found font
!end_xlist

(!B)Note:(!b)
Missing or extra spaces in the font name are ignored.

!item [(!nolink [Return]) value:]
The function returns the ID of the font, or the value 0 if no corresponding
font could be found.

!item [Availability:]
As of NVDI Version 3.02 onwards.

!item [Group:]
Inquire functions

!item [See also:]
(!link [Binding] [Bindings for vqt_name_and_id]) ~ vst_name

(!ende_liste)
!end_node



!begin_node Bindings for vqt_name_and_id
